                  <div className="max-w-[680px] text-[#1a1a1acc] text-[15px] leading-[1.65] [display:inline-block] [overflow-wrap:normal]">It stays. You can export the entire Library as Markdown, DOCX, or plain text in one click. Your account becomes read-only for ninety days, then archived, then yours forever as a single zip file.</div>
